ygData.messageBody:
Thanks for all the tips, Evulia! They are truely good advice.

*** /bows

Our biggest problems are the spawns with the really good loot just haven't
pop'ed: the New Mattress, the Undented New Range, and the Backordered New
Furniture.

*** All Backordered mobs are nasty. I camped Backordered Sofa for ages.
Eventually we just had our 'chanter turn into one.

;^)

'Nuff sillieness, back to work now...

You have gotten better at goofing off at work (59)
